<p>Choose a <a href="/wiki/Creature#Beasts" title="Creature">beast</a> that you can see. It must be able to see and hear you. If its <a href="/wiki/Ability_Scores" title="Ability Scores">Intelligence</a> is 4 or higher, the spell fails. Otherwise, it must pass a <a href="/wiki/Ability_Scores" title="Ability Scores">Wisdom</a> save or be <a href="/wiki/Conditions#Charmed" title="Conditions">charmed</a> by you. If you or one of your companions harms it, the spell ends.
</p><p><b>At Higher Levels:</b> You can target one additional beast for each slot level above 1st.
</p>
